item.title: Compiler.bat error
item.dc:creator: @pljay03 pljay03
item.description:
@pljay03 wrote:

Don’t use that compiler, all it does is confuse a shit load of people.

Simply use this:

@echo off
javac *.java
pause

If you get an error saying that Java is not recognized as an external command or something along the lines of that then go to java.sun.com and install the latest Java.
